      *@처리구분체크
      *@０１：신청번호없음
      *@０２：신청번호있음
           IF  XDJL4271-I-PRCSS-DSTIC = CO-CHA-01 OR
               XDJL4271-I-PRCSS-DSTIC = CO-CHA-02
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
      * 에러메세지 : 처리구분오류입니다．
      * 조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
               #ERROR   CO-B3000070  CO-UKJL0036  CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF

      *@채무자번호체크
           IF  XDJL4271-I-KB-PIN = SPACE
      * 에러메세지 : 필수항목미입력오류입니다．
      * 조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
               #ERROR   CO-B3800004  CO-UKJL0036  CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF
           .
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  업무처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.

220324*@   거래일 1개월전 날짜 구함
           PERFORM S3100-CJIIL03-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3100-CJIIL03-CALL-EXT

      *@1  기준일자추출
           IF XDJL4271-I-PRCSS-DSTIC = CO-CHA-01
      *@신청번호가없을때는현재설정현황조회시전영업일을기준으로조회
              MOVE JICOM-BF-BZOPR-YMD
                TO WK-BASE-YMD
           ELSE
      *@신청번호존재시포괄한도설정대상원장의ＭＡＸ（기준년월일）
      *@을추출한다．
      *@사유는신청당시에는포괄한도대상이었으나신청서출력이나과거
      *@자료조회시에는현재포괄한도대상이아닐수있으므로포괄한도
      *@대상이었던최종일을추출하여설정현황을조회한다
              PERFORM S3100-QJL2714-CALL-RTN
                 THRU S3100-QJL2714-CALL-EXT
           END-IF

      *@3  현재설정현황　추출
           PERFORM S3300-QJL1251-CALL-RTN
              THRU S3300-QJL1251-CALL-EXT

      *@4  포괄한도설정가능액　추출
           IF XDJL4271-I-PRCSS-DSTIC = CO-CHA-01
      *@      신청번호미입력
              PERFORM S3410-QJL2712-CALL-RTN
                 THRU S3410-QJL2712-CALL-EXT
           ELSE
      *@      신청번호입력
              PERFORM S3420-QJL2713-CALL-RTN
                 THRU S3420-QJL2713-CALL-EXT
           END-IF
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
220324*@  만기일/역만기일 산출(거래일 1개월전 날짜 구함)
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-CJIIL03-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE     XCJIIL03-IN

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  XCJIIL03-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *    구분코드
           MOVE  '4'
             TO  XCJIIL03-I-DSTCD
      *    년월일
           MOVE  JICOM-BF-BZOPR-YMD
            TO   XCJIIL03-I-YMD
      *    일수/월수
           MOVE  1
             TO  XCJIIL03-I-NODAY-NOMN

      *@1 공통 UTILITY CALL
           #DYCALL     CJIIL03  YCCOMMON-CA  XCJIIL03-CA

      *@1 RETURN 정보 확인
           IF  XCJIIL03-R-STAT    =  ZEROS
      *        거래일 1개월전 날짜
               MOVE  XCJIIL03-O-YMD
                 TO  WK-BASEYMD
           ELSE
               #ERROR XCJIIL03-R-ERRCD
                      XCJIIL03-R-TREAT-CD
                      XCJIIL03-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .

       S3100-CJIIL03-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  ＭＡＸ（기준년월일）구하기
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-QJL2714-CALL-RTN.

      *@1.1 초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL2714-IN
      *@1.2 호출변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL2714-I-GROUP-CO-CD
170201*@   고객식별자
           MOVE XDJL4271-I-KB-PIN
             TO XQJL2714-I-KB-PIN
      *@1.3 프로그램 호출
           #DYSQLA QJL2714 XQJL2714-CA
      *@1.4 호출결과확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
                    MOVE XQJL2714-O-BASE-YMD
                      TO WK-BASE-YMD
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
      *@원장NOT FOUND인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 원장없음오류입니다
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
                    #ERROR CO-B4200066 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3100-QJL2714-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  포괄신용공여한도　현재설정현황　조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-QJL1251-CALL-RTN.

      *@3.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL1251-IN

      *@3.2 변수 MOVE
220324*@   월말구분(1:일,2:월)
           IF WK-BASEYMD < WK-BASE-YMD
               MOVE '1'
                 TO XQJL1251-I-ENMN-DSTIC
           ELSE
               MOVE '2'
                 TO XQJL1251-I-ENMN-DSTIC
           END-IF
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL1251-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *@   기준년월일
           MOVE WK-BASE-YMD
             TO XQJL1251-I-BASE-YMD
170201*@   고객식별자
170626     MOVE XDJL4271-I-KB-PIN
             TO XQJL1251-I-KB-PIN

      *@3.3 프로그램호출
           #DYSQLA QJL1251 XQJL1251-CA

      *@3.4 호출결과확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
                    MOVE CO-CHA-1
                      TO WK-MGT-YN
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    MOVE CO-CHA-0
                      TO WK-MGT-YN
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@3.5 출력변수 MOVE
      *    채무자명
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-DBTRZ-NAME
             TO XDJL4271-O-DBTRZ-NAME
      *@   관리여부
           MOVE WK-MGT-YN
             TO XDJL4271-O-MGT-YN

220324*    포괄신용관리한도가 0이 아니면(설정상태:설정)이면
           IF XQJL1251-O-MGT-CLAM NOT = ZERO
      *@       TE여신성최고한도2011.06.03추가
               COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT
                     = FUNCTION MAX(
                       XQJL1251-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT / 1000000, 0)
      *@       포괄신용관리한도
               COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-MGT-CLAM
                     = XQJL1251-O-MGT-CLAM / 1000000
      *@       최종승인　관리한도
      *@             = MIN(TE여신성최고한도，포괄신용공여한도)
               COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT
                     = FUNCTION MAX(
                       FUNCTION MIN(XQJL1251-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT,
                                    XQJL1251-O-MGT-CLAM) / 1000000, 0)
220324*@       기사용액 = MIN(사용액, 최종적용 포괄신용공여한도)
               COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
                     = FUNCTION MAX(
                       FUNCTION MIN(
                       XQJL1251-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC / 1000000,
                       XDJL4271-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT), 0)
      *@       한도여유액＝최종승인　관리한도-기사용액
               COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
                     = XDJL4271-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT
                     - XDJL4271-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
           END-IF

      *@   계열명                                                     02184907
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
             TO XDJL4271-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME                           02185107
      *@   계열신용등급                                               02185207
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD                           02185307
             TO XDJL4271-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD                           02185407
      *@   기업신용등급                                               02185507
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1                          02185607
             TO XDJL4271-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1                          02185707
      *@   유효기일                                                   02185807
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD                            02185907
             TO XDJL4271-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD                            02186007
      *@   업종명                                                     02186107
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME                          02186207
             TO XDJL4271-O-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME                          02186307
230914*@   산업평가등급구분
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-IDSTRY-V-GRD-DSTCD
             TO XDJL4271-O-IDSTRY-V-GRD-DSTCD
           .
       S3300-QJL1251-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
