           COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-BASE-YR-ONCP-AMT
                   XDJL4271-O-AMND-B-YR-ONCP-AMT
                 = XQJL2712-O-BASE-YR-ONCP-AMT
                 / 1000000
      *@   금융비용발생차입금
           COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-FNCS-AMBR
                   XDJL4271-O-AMND-FNCS-AMBR
                 = XQJL2712-O-FNCS-AMBR
                 / 1000000
      *@   (당행차입금)
           COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-OWBNK-AMBR
                   XDJL4271-O-AMND-OWBNK-AMBR
                 = XQJL2712-O-OWBNK-AMBR
                 / 1000000
      *@   영업활동현금흐름액
           COMPUTE XDJL4271-O-BZOPR-ACF
                   XDJL4271-O-AMND-BZOPR-ACF
                 = XQJL2712-O-BZOPR-ACF
                 / 1000000
      *@   평균이자율
